Davenport.House at 2123 W. Second Street: The House at 2123 W. Second Street is a historic building located in the West End of Davenport, Iowa, United States. Before 1871 the property on which this house is located was owned by Ebenezer and Clarissa Cook, a prominent couple whose family estate was in the neighborhood. The 1½-story brick, Saltbox and Greek Revival style residence was a rarity in Davenport.
